Cediranib or placebo in combination with cisplatin and gemcitabine chemotherapy 
for patients with advanced biliary tract cancer (ABC-03): a randomised phase 2 
trial.

Valle JW(1), Wasan H(2), Lopes A(3), Backen AC(4), Palmer DH(5), Morris K(6), 
Duggan M(3), Cunningham D(7), Anthoney DA(8), Corrie P(9), Madhusudan S(10), 
Maraveyas A(11), Ross PJ(12), Waters JS(13), Steward WP(14), Rees C(15), Beare 
